# Web app (Remote Access) — Cloudflare Pages build output + wrangler local cache.
# `bun run build:web` emits dist-web/; `wrangler pages deploy` writes a .wrangler/
# cache at the repo root. Neither belongs in git. (relay/ has its own .gitignore.)
